rant-Firth-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hugh-grant">休·格兰特（Hugh Grant）</a>在<em><a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/story/hugh-grant-proust-questionnaire" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《名利场》（Vanity Fair）</a></em>的普鲁斯特（Proust）问卷中分享了他关于完美幸福的想法，并在此过程中对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/colin-firth">科林·菲斯（Colin Firth）</a>进行了厚脸皮的挖掘。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/heretic-review-hugh-grant-horror-3807614">“异端”评论：休·格兰特（Hugh Grant</a></strong></li></ul><p>当被问及他的完美幸福想法是什么时，格兰特回答说：“喝一品脱伦敦自豪感，一边嚼着小腿，阅读有关科林·菲斯（Colin Firth）的灾难和票房灾难。”</p><p>格兰特（Grant）和菲斯（Firth）在包括<em>《洛夫（Love）》（Love）</em>和<em>布里奇特·琼斯（Bridget Jones）的日记</em>在内的电影中共同努力，多年来，彼此之间轻松愉快。例如，在2022年，格兰特（Grant）用一块牌匾赞助了一把椅子，上面写着“为了纪念科林·菲斯（Colin Firth）。还没死，但看上去已经死了。由休·格兰特赞助。”</p><p>回到《<em>爱》中实际上是</em>在2003年首映的，格兰特用故意打哈欠打断了Firth采访。然而，他后来承认（通过<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/11/hugh-grant-colin-firth-box-office-bomb-perfect-happiness-1236170750/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>截止日期</em></a>）：“我从来都不是对科林很友善，但是如果说实话，他只是我真正喜欢和欣赏世界上唯一的世界演员。” </p><figure id="attachment_3811052" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3811052" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3811052" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Bridget-Jones-Cast.jpg" alt="休·格兰特，蕾妮·泽维格和科林·菲斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Bridget-Jones-Cast.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Bridget-Jones-Cast-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Bridget-Jones-Cast-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Bridget-Jones-Cast-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Bridget-Jones-Cast-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Bridget-Jones-Cast-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3811052" class="wp-caption-text"> Hugh Grant（L），Renee Zellweger（C）和Colin Firth在Photocall上摆姿势，以宣传“ Bridget Jones：理性的边缘：Adlon酒店”，2004年11月11日在德国柏林。学分：Carsten Koall/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Firth在2022年告诉<a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/hp/front/firth-why-hugh-hates-me-7234222.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>晚上的标准</em></a>：“尽管他对我的粗鲁无礼，但我还是喜欢他，我喜欢那个家伙。</p><p> “这是一个笑话，我们互相做。我一直在听到他宣布我太老了，无法再上电影院了。”</p><p>在采访中的其他地方，格兰特透露他不能使用剪刀，他不喜欢被告知通过QR码进入餐厅菜单，他最大的恐惧是带有老猫食物的猫碗“像水泥一样干燥”。</p><p>当被问及他认为是最被高估的美德时，他回答：“诚实。有时我被看过我的一部电影的人问我：“你介意我诚实吗？”我愿意。”</p><p>他还分享了他想死的方式，开玩笑说：“我的妻子同意偷偷溜到我身后，将我射在头后面。”</p><p> Grant&#39;s most recent film, <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/heretic"><em>Heretic</em></a> , was released on November 1 in the UK and November 8 in the US, and the horror thriller also follows Sophie Thatcher and Chloe East.</p><p> In <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/heretic-review-hugh-grant-horror-3807614">a four-star review, <i>NME</i> said</a> : “East and Thatcher are convincing as the Mormons who made a wrong turn and Grant is a loquacious delight in a role that could so easily have been a wad of demonic clichés. Lovers of <i>Bridget Jones&#39;s Diary</i> always knew he was a cad but this is something else entirely. He&#39;s never less than devilishly plausible and meticulous with every glance, grin and furrowed brow.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hugh-grant-says-perfect-happiness-is-a-colin-firth-box-office-flop-3811046">Hugh Grant says “perfect happiness” is a Colin Firth box office flop</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
